Revision history for Debug-Smart

0.004   2007- Kazuhiro Shibuya
        Data::Dumper turn the sortkeys option on.
        Check for write permission when open the log file.

0.003   2007-08-16 Kazuhiro Shibuya
        The opened file handle range was made narrow.
        And CLOSE mehtod is no longer available.
        Fixed TRACE method passes array arguments.

0.002   2007-08-13 Kazuhiro Shibuya
        Fixed document typo
        Fixed install dependency of Path::Class

0.001   2007-08-05 Kazuhiro Shibuya
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

